title: KSI
summary: Olajide Olayinka Williams "JJ" Olatunji (/ɒləˈdʒiːdeɪ ɒləˈtundʒiː/, oh-lah-JEE-day oh-lah-TUHN-jee; born 19 June 1993), better known as KSI, is a British YouTuber and rapper.[7] He is also a co-founder and member of the British YouTube group known as the Sidemen.[8] In 2019, he was ranked second by The Sunday Times in its list of the top 100 UK influencers.[9]
